Shaping Tomorrow's Technology Leaders

Chuiya Tech University is a premier institution of higher learning dedicated to excellence in technical education, research, and innovation. With over 250+ degree programs across 15 faculties, we prepare students for global leadership in technology and engineering.

Welcome to Chuiya Tech University

Founded in 1975, Chuiya Tech University (CTU) has established itself as a leading institution for technical education in the region. With state-of-the-art facilities, world-class faculty, and a commitment to innovation, CTU offers students an unparalleled educational experience.

25,000+ Students

From over 85 countries worldwide, creating a diverse and vibrant campus community.

1,500+ Faculty

Including Nobel laureates, industry experts, and pioneering researchers.

250+ Programs

Undergraduate, graduate, and doctoral programs across all technical disciplines.

Featured Programs

Artificial Intelligence

B.S., M.S., Ph.D.

Our AI program is ranked among the top 10 globally, with research partnerships with leading tech companies.

  • Machine Learning
  • Computer Vision
  • Natural Language Processing
  • Robotics
Learn More →

Renewable Energy Engineering

B.S., M.S.

Address global energy challenges through innovative engineering solutions for sustainable energy systems.

  • Solar Energy Systems
  • Wind Power Technology
  • Energy Storage
  • Smart Grids
Learn More →

Biomedical Engineering

B.S., M.S., Ph.D.

Combine engineering principles with medical sciences to design and create equipment, devices, and software.

  • Medical Device Design
  • Biomechanics
  • Tissue Engineering
  • Healthcare Robotics
Learn More →

About Chuiya Tech University

Our History & Mission

Established in 1975 with a vision to create a center of excellence for technical education, Chuiya Tech University has grown into one of the most respected technological universities in the world. Our mission is to advance knowledge and educate students in science, technology, and other areas of scholarship that will best serve the nation and the world in the 21st century.

We are committed to generating, disseminating, and preserving knowledge, and to working with others to bring this knowledge to bear on the world's great challenges. CTU is dedicated to providing its students with an education that combines rigorous academic study and the excitement of discovery with the support and intellectual stimulation of a diverse campus community.

Admissions

Application Process

Chuiya Tech University seeks students who demonstrate exceptional academic ability, intellectual curiosity, and the potential to contribute significantly to our campus community and the wider world.

Key Dates for 2024 Admissions

  • August 1, 2023: Application opens
  • December 15, 2023: Early decision deadline
  • February 1, 2024: Regular decision deadline
  • April 1, 2024: Admission decisions released
  • May 1, 2024: Enrollment confirmation deadline

Admission Requirements

Undergraduate Admissions

  • Completed secondary education with strong grades in mathematics and sciences
  • Standardized test scores (SAT/ACT) or equivalent
  • English language proficiency (TOEFL/IELTS) for international students
  • Personal statement and letters of recommendation
  • Extracurricular achievements and portfolio (for design programs)

Graduate Admissions

  • Bachelor's degree in a relevant field with a minimum GPA of 3.0/4.0
  • GRE/GMAT scores (program-dependent)
  • Statement of purpose and research interests
  • Letters of recommendation (typically 3)
  • Writing samples or portfolio (program-dependent)

Ready to Apply?

Begin your application to Chuiya Tech University today. Our admissions team is available to answer any questions you may have about the process.

Start Your Application

Tuition & Financial Aid

Undergraduate Tuition

$15,000/year

For domestic students. International tuition: $25,000/year

Graduate Tuition

$20,000/year

Varies by program. Most PhD programs offer full funding.

Financial Aid

65%

of students receive some form of financial assistance

Research at CTU

Chuiya Tech University is at the forefront of technological innovation and scientific discovery. Our research enterprise addresses some of the world's most pressing challenges across disciplines.

Research Centers & Institutes

  • Center for Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning
  • Institute for Sustainable Energy
  • Biomedical Engineering Research Center
  • Quantum Computing Institute
  • Center for Advanced Materials
  • Institute for Cybersecurity & Privacy
  • Robotics & Autonomous Systems Lab
  • Climate Change Research Initiative
  • Center for Data Science & Society
  • Nanotechnology Research Facility

Research Highlights

Breakthrough in Quantum Computing

CTU researchers have developed a new quantum algorithm that could revolutionize cryptography.

Sustainable Energy Storage

Our engineers have created a battery with twice the capacity of current lithium-ion batteries.

AI for Early Disease Detection

CTU's AI system can detect early signs of diseases from medical imaging with 95% accuracy.

Research Funding & Impact

25

Spin-off Companies

Research Publications/Year

Faculties & Departments

CTU is organized into 15 faculties, each housing multiple departments and research centers dedicated to advancing knowledge in their respective fields.

Faculty of Computing

Departments: Computer Science, Artificial Intelligence, Software Engineering, Information Systems, Cybersecurity

Faculty of Engineering

Departments: Mechanical, Electrical, Civil, Chemical, Biomedical, Aerospace Engineering

Faculty of Sciences

Departments: Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics, Biology, Earth Sciences, Materials Science

Faculty of Health Technology

Departments: Biomedical Engineering, Medical Informatics, Public Health Technology, Rehabilitation Sciences

Faculty of Architecture & Design

Departments: Architecture, Urban Planning, Industrial Design, Landscape Architecture

Faculty of Business Technology

Departments: Technology Management, Business Analytics, Entrepreneurship, Finance Technology
